  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292880/extras/9d1dfeee4adc5de22c7d9a37d812c487.poster.avif?t=1770427408\" width=500 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292880/extras/9d1dfeee4adc5de22c7d9a37d812c487.webm?t=1770427408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292880/extras/9d1dfeee4adc5de22c7d9a37d812c487.mp4?t=1770427408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Start with a pistol and try to erase every enemies in the area. You’re given the power to control time, you can use the bullet time management to assassinate your targets in any way you like.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292880/extras/f7727a7ddee068fa7bc1f1db4e8c1286.poster.avif?t=1770427408\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292880/extras/f7727a7ddee068fa7bc1f1db4e8c1286.webm?t=1770427408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292880/extras/f7727a7ddee068fa7bc1f1db4e8c1286.mp4?t=1770427408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 20+ levels<br></li><li>Physics environments where obstacles react realistically to the bullet<br></li><li>Bullet time twist <br></li><li>Pistol,rifle, AK, Grenade Launcher<br></li><li>Mini games<br></li><li>Supports key remapping</li></ul>",
